aos News File Format
Version 0.1

First line contains version and may not contain any spaces!

Between the ########## is an example news file.
Drop the ########## from the aos_news file.

##########
0.3.0

news text here
some more news text
...
#########

How to create a valid Aos News File:
1. safe as aos_news
2. sign: gpg --clearsign aos_news
3. test: gpg --verify aos_news.asc

Extra implementation info:

/usr/local/bin/aoscheck will find out the current installing version by:

INSTALLED_AOS_VERSION="`cat /usr/share/aos/version`"
# Remove ALL spaces.
INSTALLED_AOS_VERSION="${INSTALLED_AOS_VERSION//[[:space:]]}"

